data.text: You're The Voice: James Blunt presents ten of his absolute classic hits, arranged for piano, voice and guitar. Includes the great singles You're Beautiful, Goodbye My Lover, 1973 and seven more. The accompanying CD features full backings for each song, professionally arranged and recorded to recreate the sound of the original, so you too can sound like the real thing!
